en_151078_0	President Maithripala Sirisena said yesterday that a revolutionary change in the agro-industry would be made in the New Year.
en_151078_1	At yesterday’s meeting with Polonnaruwa District farmer’s union representatives, the President said that a large number of changes would take place with the launch of the “national programme entitled ‘three-years in a stable era” which begins today.
en_151078_2	On this occasion the President said that he hoped for the support of farmer’s with regards to this venture.
en_151078_3	Several problems faced by the farming community were made known on this occasion to which the president responded that solutions to these issues would be provided through the next series of development plans.
